resources.string: Hello, this is a new Netology! Once upon a time, Netology began with intensive courses in online marketing. Then there were courses in design, development, analytics and management. We grow by ourselves and help students grow: from beginners to confident professionals. But the most important thing remains with us: we believe that everyone has the power to want more, aim higher, and run faster. Our mission is to help us embark on the path of growth and start a chain of changes -> "https://netolo.gy/fyb"
